Class ChatData

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.am52.json.request.ChatData
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ChatData extends Object implements Serializable
The object representing the data for the chat method. The method requires the message and the sender, and if present the recipient.
